The Newton Boys;;1998;;PG-13;;Action,Crime,Drama;;6.1;;Richard Linklater;;Matthew McConaughey,Ethan Hawke,Skeet Ulrich,Vincent D'Onofrio,Gail Cronauer,Jena Karam,Casey McAuliffe,Regina Mae Matthews,Lew Temple,Dwight Yoakam,Charles Gunning,Glynn Williams,Charles 'Chip' Bray,Chloe Webb,Gary Moody,Julianna Margulies,Robert Iannaccone,Jennifer Miriam;;Four Newton brothers are a poor farmer family in the 1920s. The oldest of them, Willis, one day realizes that there's no future in the fields and offers his brothers to become a bank robbers. Soon the family agrees. They become very famous robbers, and five years later execute the greatest train robbery in American history.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120769/